These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, fanta, milk, iced-tea
Sport: volleyball, climbing, basketball, parkour
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the right of Sport:basketball##1
2. Sport:parkour is on the far left##1
3. Sport:basketball is between Sport:climbing and Beverage:fanta##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:milk is between Beverage:fanta and Beverage:almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | fanta   | milk | almond-milk       |
| Sport      | parkour | volleyball | basketball   | climbing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, writing, chess, singing
Nationality: australian, argentine, egyptian, brazilian
1. Nationality:brazilian is between Hobby:chess and Nationality:argentine##2
2. Hobby:singing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:egyptian is on the right of Nationality:australian##1
4. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the left of Nationality:australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | rock-climbing | chess | singing |
| Nationality   | argentine    | brazilian   | australian | egyptian       |

